[For a map of South Carolina go to: http://www.lib.utexas.edu/maps/united_states/south_carolina_90.jpg. Spartanburg County is on the northern border with North Carolina.

It is clear that any and all domestic animals behind in their rabies vaccinations should be vaccinated now without delay. And this should also be considered for valued livestock. - Mod MHJ

A HealthMap/ProMED-mail map can be accessed at: https://promedmail.org/promed-post?place=3657330,242.]
